WEBVTT

01:50.160 --> 01:53.930
[Love Between Lines]

01:54.410 --> 01:56.780
[Episode 8]

02:03.670 --> 02:05.030
Changing one's name...

02:06.560 --> 02:08.030
Truly pathetic.

02:10.150 --> 02:11.630
Your brother changed his name.

02:11.630 --> 02:12.960
He took my surname.

02:12.960 --> 02:14.420
His name is Xiao Zhiyu now.

02:14.710 --> 02:16.310
From now on,

02:16.460 --> 02:18.660
you can't call him by his original name.

02:21.030 --> 02:21.800
Mr. Xiao.

02:22.520 --> 02:24.400
Should we call everyone for a meeting

02:24.400 --> 02:26.990
to discuss the project requirements
Lyman just mentioned?

02:26.990 --> 02:28.520
Let's talk when we get back.

02:42.520 --> 02:43.560
Zhuling

02:43.710 --> 02:46.310
has several branch offices
in prefecture-level cities.

02:46.310 --> 02:47.840
They're small operations,

02:48.280 --> 02:50.610
perfect for someone to keep a low profile.

02:50.710 --> 02:51.710
Pick one

02:51.730 --> 02:52.990
and report there next week.

02:52.990 --> 02:54.010
Thank you, Mr. Pei.

02:54.010 --> 02:55.070
Thank you, Mr. Pei.

03:08.800 --> 03:10.560
When a dog is starved for three days,

03:10.560 --> 03:12.690
it will naturally look for leftovers.

03:13.800 --> 03:15.870
The difference between humans and dogs

03:15.870 --> 03:16.680
is that humans

03:17.560 --> 03:18.870
can't wait that long.

03:21.840 --> 03:22.560
Let's go.

03:29.010 --> 03:31.520
Why was Mr. Xiao unhappy just now?

03:31.540 --> 03:33.540
Wasn't the meeting going smoothly?

03:35.360 --> 03:38.000
That's because our opponent this time
is Zhuling again.

03:38.000 --> 03:38.800
Zhuling again?

03:38.800 --> 03:39.730
What do you mean?

03:39.800 --> 03:42.060
You just joined us, so you don't know yet.

03:42.400 --> 03:43.560
Previously, several projects at our studio

03:43.560 --> 03:44.520
were won by Mr. Xiao

03:44.520 --> 03:46.630
from Zhuling.

03:47.430 --> 03:49.710
Honestly,
we've been speculating in private

03:49.710 --> 03:51.710
that he's deliberately targeting Zhuling.

03:51.710 --> 03:53.240
But why Zhuling?

03:53.680 --> 03:55.360
Just because they're the industry leader?

03:55.360 --> 03:56.800
That we don't know.

03:56.800 --> 03:58.150
They're all big shots.

03:58.590 --> 03:59.240
Whatever conflicts they have,

03:59.240 --> 04:01.500
there's no way they'd air them publicly.

04:05.400 --> 04:06.360
Do you think

04:06.470 --> 04:08.130
what happened to Jiang Tianyi

04:08.590 --> 04:10.190
could be related to Zhuling?

04:11.510 --> 04:12.230
Could it be?

04:21.589 --> 04:23.360
[Zhuling Group]

04:30.000 --> 04:30.590
Dad!

04:32.010 --> 04:32.540
Son.

04:32.730 --> 04:33.970
Did you miss me?

04:34.310 --> 04:34.680
I did.

04:34.680 --> 04:36.560
What's got you in such a good mood?

04:36.900 --> 04:38.360
The new company registration.

04:38.360 --> 04:39.680
It was all settled today.

04:39.680 --> 04:40.620
That's wonderful.

04:40.620 --> 04:42.290
Once this current project is completed,

04:42.290 --> 04:43.950
Kanghua and I will leave the group.

04:43.950 --> 04:45.920
Dad, what's your company called?

04:47.040 --> 04:47.800
It's called...

04:47.800 --> 04:48.930
Zhuling.

04:50.630 --> 04:52.190
"Ling" means

04:52.190 --> 04:54.159
the most beautiful feathers on a bird.

04:54.159 --> 04:54.800
Xiaoyi,

04:55.200 --> 04:56.320
my company

04:56.350 --> 04:58.480
will build many grand buildings
in the future

04:58.480 --> 05:00.740
and adorn them with the finest feathers.

05:15.920 --> 05:18.120
Mr. Xiao, you're still as early as ever.

05:18.950 --> 05:21.410
Well, I don't have any old ties
to catch up on.

05:25.000 --> 05:26.360
I know what you did.

05:27.800 --> 05:30.530
And I know Jiang Tianyi
was acting on your orders.

05:31.000 --> 05:32.130
Acting on my orders?

05:32.430 --> 05:34.240
Have you ever considered that you've

05:34.240 --> 05:35.900
simply made too many enemies?

05:42.270 --> 05:44.330
Not as many as the ones you're wary of.

05:44.920 --> 05:47.040
You used Jiang Tianyi this early.

05:47.930 --> 05:50.000
Has Zhuling become nothing
but a hollow shell,

05:50.000 --> 05:51.409
so much so that you don't even dare
let me into the game?

05:51.409 --> 05:52.580
At the end of the day,

05:52.720 --> 05:54.280
you're just not very fond

05:54.300 --> 05:55.830
of my little greeting gift.

05:58.390 --> 05:59.250
How about this?

05:59.560 --> 06:01.220
Once Zhuling wins this round,

06:01.390 --> 06:02.560
whatever you want,

06:03.120 --> 06:05.120
I'll be sure to give it some thought.

06:05.270 --> 06:06.670
Over the past five years,

06:06.670 --> 06:08.670
I've heard that promise many times.

06:10.500 --> 06:12.300
I hope it can come true this time.

06:16.000 --> 06:16.680
Good luck.

06:17.680 --> 06:19.610
Not everyone is like Jiang Tianyi.

06:21.510 --> 06:22.920
Don't get too happy yet.

06:23.680 --> 06:26.610
People's hearts
aren't as unbreakable as you think.

06:43.950 --> 06:45.159
This looks nice.

06:45.159 --> 06:45.920
I haven't taken the photo yet.

06:45.920 --> 06:46.780
Drink this one.

06:47.190 --> 06:48.159
What are you doing?

06:48.159 --> 06:49.620
Updating product photos?

06:49.800 --> 06:51.000
I set up an account.

06:51.190 --> 06:53.450
I regularly update photos of our coffee.

06:54.070 --> 06:54.870
You're running an account?

06:54.870 --> 06:55.630
Didn't you say

06:55.630 --> 06:57.560
you didn't want to promote our shop?

06:57.560 --> 06:59.600
Times have changed.

07:00.340 --> 07:02.310
I've even made a business plan.

07:02.600 --> 07:03.480
Things like...

07:04.040 --> 07:05.480
the best posting frequency,

07:05.480 --> 07:07.070
trending topics,

07:07.070 --> 07:07.720
and

07:07.760 --> 07:09.070
the best times
to post for maximum traffic—

07:09.070 --> 07:10.530
I've researched them all.

07:10.800 --> 07:11.360
But

07:11.360 --> 07:12.680
the numbers just won't rise.

07:12.680 --> 07:15.240
No matter how beautiful my photos are,

07:16.040 --> 07:18.360
the best post barely gets

07:18.560 --> 07:19.510
a dozen likes.

07:20.070 --> 07:21.470
What's your account called?

07:21.470 --> 07:22.710
Regard Coffee.

07:23.630 --> 07:25.360
Regard Coffee.

07:27.750 --> 07:30.600
Be sure to like my posts
right away when I upload them.

07:30.600 --> 07:31.750
It's my dad. Hold on.

07:33.950 --> 07:34.680
Dad.

07:36.120 --> 07:37.310
Are you busy at work?

07:39.240 --> 07:40.720
Not too bad. I'm off work now.

07:40.720 --> 07:42.050
I'm at Old Zhao's place.

07:42.800 --> 07:44.040
Go home early today.

07:44.270 --> 07:45.000
Why?

07:45.270 --> 07:46.070
Your uncle

07:46.070 --> 07:47.570
sent over two boxes of crabs.

07:47.570 --> 07:48.930
One's here,

07:49.040 --> 07:50.750
and the other went to the lane.

07:50.750 --> 07:52.090
Go back early to pick them up.

07:52.090 --> 07:54.420
Crabs don't keep well
if they sit too long.

07:54.720 --> 07:56.680
Okay, I'll be home soon.

07:57.710 --> 07:58.390
Bye-bye.

08:05.210 --> 08:07.150
[Zhou Yan]

08:05.510 --> 08:06.560
Why so quiet?

08:09.040 --> 08:09.900
I'm listening.

08:12.550 --> 08:14.360
Lyman is really strict about costs,

08:14.360 --> 08:16.620
but I won't give up on the current design.

08:17.000 --> 08:17.800
Understood.

08:18.160 --> 08:20.120
I want to connect
with more building material suppliers

08:20.120 --> 08:21.920
so we can better estimate costs.

08:23.230 --> 08:25.430
Go talk to Mr. Wu of Huasheng Materials.

08:26.190 --> 08:27.720
I've worked with them before.

08:27.720 --> 08:29.250
See if they're interested.

08:30.000 --> 08:30.830
Got it.

08:35.900 --> 08:38.570
[Hu Xiu]

08:39.750 --> 08:40.390
What?

08:41.030 --> 08:42.150
Hello, Mr. Xiao.

08:42.350 --> 08:44.270
Did you get the package at your door?

08:44.270 --> 08:45.200
Those are Chongming freshwater crabs

08:45.200 --> 08:47.270
sent by my uncle.

08:47.720 --> 08:48.750
He farmed them himself.

08:48.750 --> 08:50.360
Every year, he only sets aside

08:50.360 --> 08:51.600
a small box of them from his customers.

08:51.600 --> 08:52.860
Not a single extra one.

08:53.480 --> 08:55.540
They're only available this season.

08:55.960 --> 08:58.790
My leg isn't fully healed yet,

08:58.790 --> 08:59.910
so I can't eat anything
that could cause inflammation.

08:59.910 --> 09:01.570
I can only treat you with them.

09:05.390 --> 09:06.030
Mr. Xiao?

09:06.680 --> 09:08.210
Why aren't you responding?

09:10.100 --> 09:12.560
Don't tell me you're already
steaming them.

09:14.360 --> 09:15.120
Got it.

09:21.750 --> 09:23.750
According to the geological survey report,

09:23.750 --> 09:25.200
most of this area

09:25.200 --> 09:26.670
has good foundation conditions.

09:26.670 --> 09:27.800
It belongs to Zone N.

09:27.960 --> 09:29.890
Only the southern part over there—

09:30.320 --> 09:31.550
that's Zone S.

09:33.270 --> 09:35.000
Shanghai has a lot of soft soil;

09:35.480 --> 09:36.540
it's unavoidable.

09:38.240 --> 09:39.360
That means foundation treatment costs

09:39.360 --> 09:41.510
for the southern area will be higher.

09:42.270 --> 09:43.030
I'm not sure

09:43.030 --> 09:44.960
if it will affect our overall plan.

09:50.120 --> 09:51.960
Or we could move
these 2 originally planned buildings

09:51.960 --> 09:53.000
to the south.

09:53.270 --> 09:55.150
But Mr. Xiao is a perfectionist.

09:55.370 --> 09:58.370
He'll definitely want
to rearrange the orientation.

10:01.320 --> 10:02.120
What's wrong?

10:02.630 --> 10:03.790
I'm thinking...

10:04.120 --> 10:06.000
that no matter where we build them
or how we build them,

10:06.000 --> 10:07.270
ultimately we have to consider

10:07.270 --> 10:09.270
how to deal with that soft soil area.

10:09.720 --> 10:11.320
That's another budget item.

10:12.630 --> 10:13.720
But this expense

10:13.720 --> 10:15.480
is unavoidable.

10:15.570 --> 10:16.370
That's right.

10:17.000 --> 10:18.530
Mr. Xiao always emphasizes

10:18.590 --> 10:19.490
that when it comes to designing,

10:19.490 --> 10:21.660
safety issues are non-negotiable.

10:22.430 --> 10:24.320
We definitely need to consider
soil replacement.

10:24.320 --> 10:26.780
It's to thoroughly improve the foundation.

10:27.270 --> 10:29.720
But soil replacement
requires a lot of labor,

10:29.720 --> 10:31.870
and our design costs are already high.

10:34.720 --> 10:36.120
It's quite challenging.

10:42.390 --> 10:43.510
You are nervous?

10:44.750 --> 10:45.870
What are you talking about?

10:45.870 --> 10:47.000
Aren't you nervous?

10:49.320 --> 10:50.790
I'm... I'm fine.

10:51.120 --> 10:53.520
You know our competitor is Zhuling, right?

10:54.480 --> 10:55.150
Yes, I know.

10:57.630 --> 10:59.030
You're quite something.

10:59.240 --> 11:00.750
I'm impressed, Hu Xiu.

11:01.270 --> 11:03.070
You've got quite strong nerves.

11:03.550 --> 11:05.720
I believe in Mr. Xiao's design.

11:06.750 --> 11:07.670
Of course.

11:07.670 --> 11:08.800
I believe in him too.

11:09.270 --> 11:10.320
Mr. Xiao's designs

11:10.320 --> 11:11.720
have always been unique.

11:11.750 --> 11:13.600
After competing with Zhuling
for so many years,

11:13.600 --> 11:15.930
we're not necessarily at a disadvantage.

11:24.870 --> 11:26.200
But Zhuling...

11:26.550 --> 11:28.000
is a big, well-established company.

11:28.000 --> 11:29.800
Their strengths lie elsewhere.

11:29.960 --> 11:30.840
Secretary Li.

11:31.510 --> 11:32.080
Thank you for coming.

11:32.080 --> 11:32.840
Mr. Pei.

11:32.870 --> 11:33.870
Please, this way.

11:34.200 --> 11:35.130
Watch your step.

11:36.120 --> 11:37.750
The environment here is quite nice.

11:37.750 --> 11:38.390
Yes.

11:38.960 --> 11:41.360
We plan to utilize
the entire water system.

11:42.720 --> 11:45.250
That person
is from the Construction Bureau.

11:46.440 --> 11:47.390
The area we're looking at now

11:47.390 --> 11:48.720
is the core landscape zone.

11:48.720 --> 11:51.380
Supporting facilities
will be at the entrance.

11:56.550 --> 11:58.630
Try as much as you can to avoid the part

11:58.630 --> 12:00.150
where clay is under the water.

12:00.150 --> 12:01.810
The foundation must be solid.

12:03.870 --> 12:05.550
So Zhuling's advantage

12:05.790 --> 12:07.050
is their connections.

12:07.390 --> 12:09.240
Having connections makes things easier.

12:09.240 --> 12:11.300
And it helps keep project costs down.

12:11.440 --> 12:12.720
Like I just said,

12:12.830 --> 12:14.200
Mr. Xiao's skills are top-notch,

12:14.200 --> 12:16.330
but the corresponding costs are high.

12:16.540 --> 12:17.990
In terms of cost-effectiveness,

12:17.990 --> 12:19.450
we might not have the edge.

12:20.510 --> 12:22.270
So the only thing we can rely on

12:23.000 --> 12:24.600
is Mr. Xiao's design?

12:26.360 --> 12:27.120
Right.

12:30.560 --> 12:31.370
Good luck.

12:33.130 --> 12:33.920
Take this.

12:42.000 --> 12:42.770
If that's the case,

12:42.770 --> 12:44.170
this area will be wasted.

12:45.260 --> 12:46.720
We need to do it over there,

12:46.960 --> 12:48.510
because it allows for future extension.

12:48.510 --> 12:49.640
The other side is...

12:55.170 --> 12:56.130
Hello, Ms. Zhou.

12:58.320 --> 12:59.170
A meeting?

13:00.150 --> 13:01.030
Now?

13:03.000 --> 13:03.870
I'm on the site.

13:05.090 --> 13:05.690
It's fine.

13:06.310 --> 13:07.440
We'll head back now.

13:08.360 --> 13:09.220
What happened?

13:09.790 --> 13:11.650
Some details in the previous plan

13:11.870 --> 13:14.400
aren't fully aligned
with Ms. Zhou's budget.

13:14.670 --> 13:16.000
Mr. Xiao and Ms. Zhou
need to have a meeting

13:16.000 --> 13:17.460
to reconfirm everything.

13:17.550 --> 13:19.080
We need to get back quickly.

13:20.480 --> 13:21.630
You go back first.

13:22.670 --> 13:23.530
I'll stay here.

13:23.870 --> 13:24.630
It's getting late.

13:24.630 --> 13:26.230
Is it okay for you to be alone?

13:26.960 --> 13:28.720
Since I'm already here, and...

13:29.320 --> 13:30.980
based on the materials I have,

13:31.000 --> 13:33.360
the difference between the site elevation

13:33.360 --> 13:34.940
and the road elevation on-site
is a bit large.

13:34.940 --> 13:36.400
I want to measure it again.

13:37.510 --> 13:38.270
You go back.

13:38.840 --> 13:39.570
And this too.

13:40.000 --> 13:40.480
Here.

13:43.200 --> 13:44.060
I can handle it.

13:44.120 --> 13:45.180
You're excellent.

13:45.720 --> 13:46.580
I am excellent.

13:48.220 --> 13:49.550
Be careful on your own.

13:49.570 --> 13:50.210
Okay.

13:50.350 --> 13:51.750
Call me when you get home.

13:52.170 --> 13:56.470
♪ Under the streetlight,
I grow increasingly weary ♪

13:58.260 --> 14:03.100
♪ A few specks of dust
drift by in the wind ♪

13:59.670 --> 14:00.790
Does anyone have any different ideas?

14:00.790 --> 14:01.790
Feel free to share.

14:01.790 --> 14:02.510
Mr. Xiao.

14:02.720 --> 14:04.910
We have these ideas
for the three-dimensional

14:04.910 --> 14:06.000
decision-making model:

14:05.380 --> 14:09.540
♪ The girl who once
basked in the sunlight ♪

14:06.390 --> 14:06.790
first,

14:07.000 --> 14:08.080
cultural symbolism.

14:08.080 --> 14:09.740
Through patterns, colors...

14:10.220 --> 14:13.140
♪ Where did she go to play? ♪

14:13.120 --> 14:14.630
Come on, let's go take a look up ahead.

14:13.580 --> 14:16.560
♪ I don't understand either ♪

14:18.790 --> 14:22.620
♪ Flicking through old chat logs ♪

14:24.880 --> 14:29.760
♪ I just realized the replies
were somewhat delayed ♪

14:30.900 --> 14:36.890
♪ At the crossroads of choices,
amidst the bustling crowd ♪

14:38.780 --> 14:45.850
♪ Who hasn't paid the price
and still fallen short? ♪

14:45.890 --> 14:50.440
♪ Stand with me tonight,
look at the starlight ♪

14:51.180 --> 14:56.600
♪ Even if we're always
pushed aside by reality ♪

14:57.860 --> 15:04.520
♪ I know the dark clouds will still come ♪

15:04.770 --> 15:10.890
♪ But in this world,
there will always be someone ♪

15:13.710 --> 15:18.220
♪ Who looks forward
with the same hope as me ♪

15:18.870 --> 15:19.550
Thank you.

15:20.080 --> 15:21.480
Where's your colleague?

15:22.040 --> 15:23.560
He had to leave early.

15:25.480 --> 15:27.210
How about I give you a ride home?

15:27.910 --> 15:28.630
It's fine.

15:29.090 --> 15:30.020
I'll take a taxi.

15:31.670 --> 15:32.320
Thanks.

15:54.110 --> 15:55.640
It's hard to get a taxi here,

15:55.700 --> 15:56.950
and it's raining now.

15:59.420 --> 16:00.380
I'll wait.

16:00.850 --> 16:02.180
I can go to the main road.

16:04.440 --> 16:06.170
Ms. Hu, do you dislike me?

16:10.540 --> 16:11.300
I...

16:11.600 --> 16:13.040
Given the relationship
between our two companies,

16:13.040 --> 16:13.980
I completely understand if you want

16:13.980 --> 16:15.470
to keep your distance from me.

16:15.470 --> 16:16.800
But for safety reasons,

16:16.940 --> 16:18.250
there's no way I, a grown man,

16:18.250 --> 16:19.720
would let a girl

16:19.920 --> 16:21.070
stay here alone.

16:22.920 --> 16:23.980
Let's go together.

16:34.340 --> 16:34.890
Hu Xiu,

16:34.940 --> 16:35.650
are you home?

16:35.650 --> 16:37.480
It looks like it's raining outside.

16:37.480 --> 16:38.210
Don't worry.

16:38.360 --> 16:39.620
I'm already in the car.

16:40.240 --> 16:40.740
Alright.

16:40.740 --> 16:42.380
Then let me know when you get home.

16:42.380 --> 16:43.140
It's Hu Xiu?

16:44.090 --> 16:45.350
What's wrong with her?

16:45.420 --> 16:46.970
Didn't I go to the site today?

16:46.970 --> 16:48.340
I couldn't find an assistant at the time,

16:48.340 --> 16:49.800
so I asked her to go with me.

16:50.080 --> 16:51.150
She's not back yet?

16:51.150 --> 16:52.360
She insisted on staying there

16:52.360 --> 16:53.650
to verify the elevation differences
on site.

16:53.650 --> 16:55.870
But she just said
she's already in the car.

16:55.870 --> 16:56.910
Okay, I got it.

16:57.840 --> 16:58.510
Sun,

16:58.660 --> 17:00.790
you really don't go easy on newcomers.

17:01.360 --> 17:02.270
Hu Xiu has been here for so long.

17:02.270 --> 17:03.670
She's hardly a newcomer anymore.

17:03.670 --> 17:05.130
Besides, you have no idea,

17:05.240 --> 17:07.020
but the people from Zhuling
were also there today.

17:07.020 --> 17:08.150
It was quite a scene.

17:09.220 --> 17:10.060
Young man,

17:10.310 --> 17:12.369
you should feel some sense of crisis.

17:13.099 --> 17:13.760
Get to work.

17:27.470 --> 17:29.530
Ms. Hu, you don't need to be so formal.

17:29.640 --> 17:30.590
Actually,

17:30.990 --> 17:32.790
we should have been colleagues.

17:33.960 --> 17:34.920
How did you know?

17:35.310 --> 17:36.830
An outstanding candidate like you

17:36.830 --> 17:38.670
certainly leaves a deep impression.

17:38.670 --> 17:39.910
It's just a pity

17:40.960 --> 17:42.960
that you didn't choose us in the end.

17:45.680 --> 17:46.960
Being able to interview at Zhuling

17:46.960 --> 17:48.070
was an honor.

17:48.260 --> 17:50.430
It was just that my career goals

17:50.590 --> 17:53.450
might not have fully aligned
with Zhuling's needs.

17:55.740 --> 17:56.940
That was our mistake.

17:57.240 --> 17:59.720
HR's assessment of you was off.

18:01.010 --> 18:02.290
If possible,

18:02.850 --> 18:04.020
I wonder if you'd be willing to

18:04.020 --> 18:05.830
give me another chance.

18:07.120 --> 18:08.520
You're too kind, Mr. Pei.

18:08.680 --> 18:09.920
I'm already really grateful

18:09.920 --> 18:11.780
that you drove me back in the rain.

18:15.720 --> 18:16.810
It was no trouble.

18:17.790 --> 18:18.680
As a boss,

18:18.790 --> 18:20.070
I would never leave my employee

18:20.070 --> 18:21.270
alone at the site.

18:22.720 --> 18:23.510
Indeed.

18:23.960 --> 18:26.220
My colleague wanted me to leave with him.

18:26.290 --> 18:28.730
It was my fault—
I just wanted to hurry a bit.

18:29.830 --> 18:30.750
Sounds like you've been

18:30.750 --> 18:31.510
fairly happy

18:31.510 --> 18:32.750
at Dynamism.

18:33.960 --> 18:34.640
Of course.

18:34.880 --> 18:35.960
After all, working in this field

18:35.960 --> 18:37.510
has always been my dream.

18:37.880 --> 18:38.550
And Dynamism

18:38.550 --> 18:39.160
is a

18:39.160 --> 18:40.560
very open-minded place.

18:42.280 --> 18:43.080
Open-minded?

18:44.590 --> 18:45.720
What about Mr. Xiao?

18:46.200 --> 18:47.460
Is he open-minded too?

18:48.590 --> 18:50.310
Even before I started working,

18:50.310 --> 18:52.040
I already admired his designs.

18:56.510 --> 18:58.240
Mr. Xiao is young and talented.

18:58.830 --> 19:00.490
He's always been impressive.

19:13.220 --> 19:14.150
Are you alright?

19:20.250 --> 19:22.850
♪ I wanted you to see the light ♪

19:24.840 --> 19:27.210
♪ But you tried to shut it down ♪

19:27.230 --> 19:30.040
♪ That night ♪

19:31.310 --> 19:33.940
♪ I know I should be dreaming ♪

19:35.730 --> 19:38.010
♪ But I'm still standing here ♪

19:38.330 --> 19:40.770
♪ Trying to take in reality ♪

19:41.270 --> 19:47.330
♪ Just wanna let this storm calm down ♪

19:42.920 --> 19:43.780
Get off the car.

19:48.780 --> 19:51.620
♪ But I can not sleep ♪

19:52.130 --> 19:56.860
♪ Because I'm done pretending ♪

19:57.240 --> 19:59.240
♪ And I ♪

19:59.650 --> 20:01.770
♪ I'm ready, I won't hide ♪

20:01.790 --> 20:04.220
♪ Now it's my turn ♪

20:02.960 --> 20:03.790
Mr. Xiao,

20:04.070 --> 20:05.310
you're quite timely.

20:05.250 --> 20:07.720
♪ The reality is boring ♪

20:05.440 --> 20:06.070
What?

20:06.090 --> 20:08.190
Are you afraid I'll poach your employee?

20:08.190 --> 20:11.470
♪ Following all the rules ♪

20:08.790 --> 20:10.250
Zhuling is full of elites.

20:10.790 --> 20:12.720
Surely you wouldn't need
to poach a junior designer.

20:11.980 --> 20:15.670
♪ So I'll just break it ♪

20:15.310 --> 20:16.110
Ms. Hu,

20:16.270 --> 20:17.440
it seems your Mr. Xiao

20:16.540 --> 20:18.950
♪ I'm free ♪

20:17.550 --> 20:19.150
doesn't have much confidence in you.

20:19.150 --> 20:21.760
♪ A new interpretation ♪

20:22.110 --> 20:22.740
Bye.

20:22.860 --> 20:26.380
♪ Dreams contend with waking hours ♪

20:27.260 --> 20:29.340
♪ Even if fate ♪

20:29.910 --> 20:32.880
♪ Cycles on and on ♪

20:33.780 --> 20:37.610
♪ How many tales tomorrow will spawn ♪

20:38.110 --> 20:40.520
♪ I'm free ♪

20:40.620 --> 20:43.930
♪ Winner still unknown ♪

20:44.560 --> 20:48.080
♪ I'll be the one writing my own story ♪

20:51.130 --> 20:51.810
Mr. Xiao,

20:52.400 --> 20:54.130
why did you suddenly come here?

20:55.820 --> 20:56.840
[Mr. Wu]

20:58.960 --> 20:59.590
Mr. Wu,

21:00.100 --> 21:01.030
long time no see.

21:01.680 --> 21:02.200
Yes,

21:02.270 --> 21:04.000
I asked Zhou Yan to contact you.

21:12.350 --> 21:14.940
The park's identification system
often malfunctions.

21:14.940 --> 21:15.900
I'll walk back.

21:17.270 --> 21:18.110
I'll get an umbrella

21:18.110 --> 21:19.510
and walk you downstairs.

21:25.640 --> 21:27.970
The Lyman project is very important to us.

21:29.110 --> 21:31.160
I don't want any mistakes to happen.

21:31.790 --> 21:32.510
Of course.

21:32.530 --> 21:35.060
That's why
we went to check out the site today.

21:36.820 --> 21:37.750
What I mean is...

21:38.260 --> 21:39.990
as a member of the project team,

21:40.110 --> 21:42.170
you should keep a distance from them.

21:43.960 --> 21:45.370
Today I got into Mr. Pei's car

21:45.370 --> 21:46.720
only because it was raining

21:46.720 --> 21:48.120
and I couldn't get a taxi.

21:49.000 --> 21:49.830
I'm sorry, Mr. Xiao.

21:49.830 --> 21:51.490
I wasn't thinking it through.

21:53.300 --> 21:56.100
You've probably heard about Jiang Tianyi,
right?

21:56.350 --> 21:58.610
Zhuling is definitely involved in this.

21:58.700 --> 21:59.810
During this project,

21:59.810 --> 22:02.070
it's best to stay away from their people.

22:04.920 --> 22:06.070
So, Mr. Xiao,

22:07.070 --> 22:08.680
you came to the site

22:08.880 --> 22:10.410
because you don't trust me?

22:10.980 --> 22:11.480
I...

22:14.760 --> 22:15.980
[Zhou Yan]

22:27.350 --> 22:27.910
Yes.

22:28.510 --> 22:30.840
Mr. Wu from Huasheng Materials called me.

22:36.100 --> 22:37.660
What did the supplier say?

22:43.030 --> 22:44.400
Then I will need you and He

22:44.400 --> 22:46.230
to go on a trip out of town.

22:47.310 --> 22:48.840
Alright, that's it for now.

23:22.830 --> 23:24.070
Am I so untrustworthy

23:24.510 --> 23:26.070
in his eyes?

23:46.770 --> 23:49.160
[Solara Tech]

23:47.550 --> 23:48.510
If I'd known they wouldn't be here,

23:48.510 --> 23:50.710
I wouldn't have brought so many dishes.

23:54.720 --> 23:55.850
Don't mention them.

23:55.920 --> 23:57.400
They were all exhausted.

23:58.070 --> 23:59.310
I sent them all home.

24:03.830 --> 24:05.690
You ordered so many dishes today?

24:06.000 --> 24:06.830
Ms. Zhao,

24:08.720 --> 24:09.980
did you land a big deal?

24:10.830 --> 24:12.160
I'm in a good mood today.

24:13.270 --> 24:15.870
Didn't the park say
they were going to raise the rent before?

24:15.870 --> 24:16.410
I took care of it.

24:16.410 --> 24:17.440
They won't do it now.

24:17.440 --> 24:18.770
How did you manage that?

24:18.790 --> 24:19.880
I negotiated a cooperation

24:19.880 --> 24:21.030
with the park.

24:21.350 --> 24:22.960
In the future,
when the companies in there hold events,

24:22.960 --> 24:24.480
I can provide catering

24:24.480 --> 24:25.960
and venue support.

24:26.260 --> 24:26.870
The costs—

24:27.090 --> 24:28.270
have you checked the costs?

24:28.270 --> 24:28.920
Of course.

24:28.920 --> 24:30.850
I never do business at a loss, okay?

24:32.410 --> 24:33.470
I've been thinking

24:34.030 --> 24:36.660
we could make
employee membership cards for them.

24:36.660 --> 24:38.880
There are so many holidays
throughout the year.

24:38.880 --> 24:39.750
Our shop's cards

24:39.750 --> 24:42.210
could totally be used
as employee benefits.

24:43.220 --> 24:44.220
What do you think?

24:45.100 --> 24:45.830
Impressive.

24:46.890 --> 24:48.040
So,

24:48.070 --> 24:49.160
there's no need to be stressed.

24:49.160 --> 24:50.670
Everything can be solved.

24:54.640 --> 24:55.400
Honey,

24:56.510 --> 24:57.920
since you're so smart,

24:58.720 --> 25:01.000
I have a problem of my own lately.

25:01.020 --> 25:02.680
Could you help me solve it too?

25:03.200 --> 25:04.060
I'm listening.

25:04.240 --> 25:05.910
Come with me
to play a murder mystery game.

25:05.910 --> 25:08.010
You want to play murder mystery games?

25:08.010 --> 25:09.730
I'm discussing a project.

25:09.830 --> 25:10.480
That client

25:10.480 --> 25:11.830
wants us to develop

25:11.830 --> 25:13.310
a business park
management software product.

25:13.310 --> 25:14.110
When I asked further,

25:14.110 --> 25:15.310
I found out he's from Fangyun Group—

25:15.310 --> 25:17.740
the one in charge
of your park's operations.

25:17.740 --> 25:18.960
He's just been transferred there

25:18.960 --> 25:20.510
and is extremely interested

25:20.510 --> 25:21.910
in murder mystery games.

25:22.110 --> 25:24.200
So you want to take him to play?

25:24.440 --> 25:24.960
Yes.

25:25.950 --> 25:28.550
But I know nothing
about murder mystery games.

25:28.990 --> 25:31.190
I'm afraid it might get awkward by then.

25:31.240 --> 25:33.210
What's so hard about playing a game?

25:33.210 --> 25:33.760
Here's the plan:

25:33.760 --> 25:35.160
let's call Hu Xiu along.

25:35.190 --> 25:36.160
More people means more fun.

25:36.160 --> 25:37.640
She's way more experienced than I am now.

25:37.640 --> 25:39.310
That would be wonderful.

25:40.110 --> 25:40.720
Honey.

25:41.400 --> 25:42.350
You're the best.

25:44.400 --> 25:46.520
The food you prepared today is delicious.

25:46.520 --> 25:47.650
Then have some more.

25:53.820 --> 25:54.660
Mr. Xiao.

26:05.600 --> 26:08.030
The southern part near the river
is all soft soil.

26:08.030 --> 26:09.480
Foundation treatment costs will be high.

26:09.480 --> 26:11.470
I think what Sun said before has a point.

26:11.470 --> 26:13.110
Why don't we move
the detached houses in the plan

26:13.110 --> 26:14.570
over to the southern part?

26:14.720 --> 26:16.400
What about the orientation and lighting?

26:16.400 --> 26:17.920
Orientation can be adjusted.

26:17.920 --> 26:20.030
Having the side facing the water
is actually not a problem.

26:20.030 --> 26:20.750
The most important thing

26:20.750 --> 26:23.550
is to make the waterfront concept
work to its fullest.

26:23.550 --> 26:25.270
In Shanghai's modern architecture,

26:25.270 --> 26:27.480
there are many riverside buildings,

26:27.590 --> 26:28.750
but most

26:28.750 --> 26:30.950
have a certain distance from the water.

26:31.150 --> 26:33.080
Designs like a fitness path
along the river

26:33.080 --> 26:33.920
are too conventional,

26:33.920 --> 26:36.270
and they don't fit the lane-style elements
we're aiming for.

26:36.270 --> 26:37.720
You mean...

26:38.010 --> 26:39.140
waterfront lanes?

26:39.410 --> 26:39.960
Yes.

26:40.160 --> 26:41.230
In Shanghai,

26:41.250 --> 26:43.210
most lanes are in the city center.

26:43.400 --> 26:45.210
Apart from some nearby ancient towns,

26:45.210 --> 26:47.400
waterfront lanes are actually very rare.

26:47.400 --> 26:49.400
Since Lyman's site is by the water,

26:49.510 --> 26:50.550
we could consider

26:50.550 --> 26:52.200
this kind of waterside-perching layout,

26:52.200 --> 26:55.260
creating a contemporary version
of a waterfront lane.

26:59.180 --> 27:01.240
This proposal is worth considering.

27:02.210 --> 27:03.810
It has practical potential.

27:07.480 --> 27:08.160
Hu Xiu,

27:08.680 --> 27:10.310
your ideas are bold,

27:10.420 --> 27:12.100
but they're very creative.

27:12.880 --> 27:14.010
Thank you, Ms. Zhou.

27:14.080 --> 27:15.740
Boldness brings innovation.

27:16.110 --> 27:17.160
At Dynamism,

27:17.160 --> 27:19.420
there's no need to stick to conventions.

27:22.350 --> 27:23.210
Well, Ms. Zhou,

27:23.220 --> 27:24.620
I'll get back to work now.

27:32.200 --> 27:33.440
Not bad, this girl.

27:34.030 --> 27:36.080
She keeps her emotions in check.

27:36.270 --> 27:36.950
Yesterday,

27:36.980 --> 27:38.750
seeing so many people
from Zhuling go there

27:38.750 --> 27:40.590
and how they have connections
to the Construction Bureau,

27:40.590 --> 27:41.920
she was really worried.

27:41.920 --> 27:43.350
She insisted on checking and verifying

27:43.350 --> 27:45.750
all the site conditions before going home.

27:47.650 --> 27:49.040
Alright, let's settle on this for now.

27:49.040 --> 27:50.440
Next, I'll handle the coordination.

27:50.440 --> 27:51.830
Mr. Xiao, Ms. Zhou, see you tomorrow.

27:51.830 --> 27:52.700
Goodbye.

27:54.640 --> 27:55.440
What's wrong?

27:57.920 --> 27:58.510
Nothing.

28:12.310 --> 28:14.440
Why are you still working after hours?

28:15.390 --> 28:16.700
I need to grow up

28:16.720 --> 28:18.300
in the shortest time possible.

28:18.300 --> 28:20.230
I want those who don't believe in me

28:20.320 --> 28:22.180
to see what I'm really capable of.

28:23.960 --> 28:25.550
What upset you this time?

28:27.590 --> 28:28.150
Nothing.

28:29.510 --> 28:31.370
You need to balance work and rest.

28:31.700 --> 28:32.170
How about this?

28:32.170 --> 28:33.110
Wang is taking his client

28:33.110 --> 28:34.590
to a murder mystery game tonight.

28:34.590 --> 28:35.350
Let's join them,

28:35.350 --> 28:36.410
just to relax a bit.

28:38.600 --> 28:40.560
Can I skip it?

28:41.290 --> 28:43.040
Wang is going there for business.

28:43.040 --> 28:44.790
It'll be boring for me if I go alone.

28:44.790 --> 28:46.530
Didn't you like playing that game before?

28:46.530 --> 28:47.990
Just come with me, please?

28:48.990 --> 28:51.750
I had a falling out with Qin Xiaoyi there.

28:51.770 --> 28:53.530
It'll be awkward if I see him.

28:54.960 --> 28:56.790
When I went to the club
to pick up the tickets today,

28:56.790 --> 28:57.880
it was Li Yue there.

28:57.880 --> 28:59.610
It should be his session today.

29:00.290 --> 29:00.940
Li Yue?

29:07.160 --> 29:08.160
Fine, I'll go.

29:09.090 --> 29:10.090
That's my friend.

29:14.000 --> 29:15.400
Are these the most expensive beans?

29:15.400 --> 29:16.200
Yes.

29:18.300 --> 29:18.870
Mr. Qian.

29:19.160 --> 29:19.710
Mr. Guangming.

29:19.710 --> 29:20.740
Just call me Qian.

29:20.960 --> 29:21.820
Alright, Qian.

29:22.310 --> 29:23.440
I brought you some coffee.

29:23.440 --> 29:24.000
Thanks.

29:24.680 --> 29:25.680
Let me introduce you.

29:25.680 --> 29:26.810
This is Qian Jinxin.

29:27.000 --> 29:29.730
He's in charge
of operations for the entire park.

29:29.830 --> 29:30.690
This is my wife,

29:30.880 --> 29:31.680
Zhao Xiaorou.

29:31.680 --> 29:32.240
The café

29:32.240 --> 29:32.590
across the street,

29:32.590 --> 29:33.160
Regard,

29:33.240 --> 29:34.070
is hers.

29:35.070 --> 29:36.790
I saw it when I passed by earlier.

29:36.790 --> 29:37.650
It's very nice.

29:37.880 --> 29:39.940
Thanks. Feel free to drop by anytime.

29:40.790 --> 29:41.650
And who is this?

29:42.070 --> 29:43.330
My best friend, Hu Xiu.

29:44.790 --> 29:45.240
Hello.

29:45.790 --> 29:46.350
Hello.

29:47.710 --> 29:48.910
Let's go get our tickets checked first.

29:48.910 --> 29:49.460
Sure.

29:49.670 --> 29:50.870
Let's check in first.

29:52.720 --> 29:53.160
Honey,

29:53.830 --> 29:54.920
teach me how to play now.

29:54.920 --> 29:57.120
I don't want to embarrass myself later.

30:05.120 --> 30:05.840
Ms. Hu,

30:06.310 --> 30:07.000
you have such elegant poise.

30:07.000 --> 30:08.530
Did you study dance before?

30:09.280 --> 30:10.000
No.

30:11.730 --> 30:13.940
You should explore more in the arts.

30:14.350 --> 30:15.480
You're so young.

30:15.760 --> 30:18.040
You should try more new things.

30:19.300 --> 30:20.500
You're really funny.

30:21.030 --> 30:22.270
I'm not joking.

30:23.750 --> 30:24.880
Alright, players for the next session,

30:24.880 --> 30:26.240
you may start choosing your boxes now.

30:26.240 --> 30:26.880
Attention,

30:26.880 --> 30:27.440
drinks

30:27.440 --> 30:28.790
are not allowed in the game area.

30:28.790 --> 30:29.920
If you need to store them,

30:29.920 --> 30:31.520
there's a locker over there.

30:36.590 --> 30:37.110
Qian!

30:37.790 --> 30:38.520
Choose a box.

30:41.480 --> 30:43.340
What were you guys talking about?

30:43.440 --> 30:44.270
Nothing.

30:44.430 --> 30:46.230
Is that guy Guangming's client?

30:46.840 --> 30:48.680
They're discussing a collaboration.

30:48.680 --> 30:49.550
Qian Jinxin

30:49.550 --> 30:51.550
was recently transferred to this park.

30:51.550 --> 30:52.960
He wants Wang to develop

30:52.960 --> 30:54.510
a park management software product
for him.

30:54.510 --> 30:56.750
Later,
things like access control, parking,

30:56.750 --> 30:57.750
and property management

30:57.750 --> 30:59.860
can all be handled through this software.

30:59.860 --> 31:01.120
How do you know so much?

31:02.360 --> 31:03.290
I have no choice.

31:03.480 --> 31:05.020
Wang is in the early stage of his startup.

31:05.020 --> 31:06.790
I want to provide all the support I can,

31:06.790 --> 31:08.000
and help him secure

31:08.000 --> 31:09.330
any potential clients.

31:10.030 --> 31:10.640
Let's go.

31:10.660 --> 31:11.990
Let's go pick our boxes.

31:20.020 --> 31:21.150
Ms. Hu! Ms. Hu!

31:21.270 --> 31:22.270
Ms. Hu, let's go together.

31:22.270 --> 31:23.270
Rongcheng is too dangerous.

31:23.270 --> 31:23.510
No need.

31:23.510 --> 31:24.870
Let's not get separated.

31:24.870 --> 31:25.400
It's fine.

31:25.400 --> 31:26.000
No need.

31:26.740 --> 31:27.540
I'm sorry.

31:39.960 --> 31:40.680
What?

31:41.160 --> 31:43.490
Is this a welcome gift for me
in Rongcheng?

31:54.980 --> 31:55.870
Why is it you?

31:56.880 --> 31:57.940
You're surprised?

31:59.200 --> 31:59.960
This is my wife.

31:59.960 --> 32:00.960
I haven't been able to keep her in line.

32:00.960 --> 32:01.760
My apologies.

32:11.710 --> 32:12.510
Mr. Qian.

32:12.960 --> 32:14.590
Reporter Han Yingzhi and Mr. Miyazaki

32:14.590 --> 32:15.720
are indeed married,

32:15.720 --> 32:17.480
but it's a fake marriage.

32:17.720 --> 32:18.440
I understand.

32:18.440 --> 32:19.770
Like Mr. and Mrs. Smith.

32:20.270 --> 32:21.400
Though compared to Angelina Jolie,

32:21.400 --> 32:23.030
you're missing

32:23.180 --> 32:25.210
a little bit of that sexy factor.

32:25.640 --> 32:27.030
Although we're on different sides,

32:27.030 --> 32:28.790
the people we're up against are the same,

32:28.790 --> 32:29.350
right?

32:29.350 --> 32:31.080
Let me see your character card.

32:31.160 --> 32:32.160
-Let me see.
-Xiu.

32:35.030 --> 32:35.560
How is it?

32:36.180 --> 32:36.830
Not bad.

32:37.800 --> 32:38.510
Guy,

32:39.160 --> 32:40.220
it's getting late.

32:40.530 --> 32:41.930
Let's head into the city.

32:42.940 --> 32:43.580
Let's go.

32:43.750 --> 32:44.400
Let's go.

32:45.000 --> 32:45.460
Please.

33:00.150 --> 33:01.830
Well, well, well, Reporter Han,

33:01.830 --> 33:03.960
I've heard so much about you.

33:04.930 --> 33:05.990
What's my mission?

33:08.260 --> 33:09.190
I need you

33:09.210 --> 33:10.350
to get close to Qin Xiaoyi

33:10.350 --> 33:11.680
under the pretense of an interview

33:11.680 --> 33:13.760
and steal his pocket watch.

33:14.550 --> 33:15.350
Pocket watch?

33:15.570 --> 33:17.960
I found a very important lead.

33:18.200 --> 33:20.920
Qin Xiaoyi's father
was an economic criminal.

33:20.970 --> 33:22.940
That pocket watch is his heirloom.

33:23.750 --> 33:25.920
Once we expose his background,

33:25.940 --> 33:29.020
he'll be finished.

33:38.640 --> 33:39.840
Don't rush.

33:39.950 --> 33:42.080
He's at the theater. He can't get away.

33:44.360 --> 33:45.150
Ms. Hu!

33:45.750 --> 33:46.400
Ms. Hu!

33:46.680 --> 33:47.200
Ms. Hu!

33:48.110 --> 33:48.920
Ms. Hu.

33:49.430 --> 33:51.290
Looks like I wasn't mistaken earlier.

33:51.290 --> 33:52.620
You did go to the casino.

33:53.160 --> 33:53.880
Ms. Hu,

33:54.310 --> 33:55.480
as a young woman,

33:55.510 --> 33:56.860
it's not really appropriate for you

33:56.860 --> 33:58.680
to keep going to places like that.

33:58.680 --> 33:59.550
Mr. Qian,

33:59.570 --> 34:01.770
in Rongcheng, players can go anywhere.

34:01.920 --> 34:02.830
I understand.

34:03.070 --> 34:04.550
Then let me take you somewhere fun.

34:04.550 --> 34:06.210
No thanks, I've got a mission.

34:07.450 --> 34:08.489
It's just nearby.

34:09.510 --> 34:10.909
When I passed by earlier,

34:10.920 --> 34:12.230
I saw a clothing store.

34:12.880 --> 34:13.719
Actually,

34:13.760 --> 34:15.150
I wanted to tell you this

34:15.150 --> 34:16.760
right after we got off the train.

34:16.760 --> 34:18.190
The outfit you picked

34:18.620 --> 34:21.230
is a bit outdated.

34:21.840 --> 34:22.760
But it's okay.

34:23.070 --> 34:24.730
We can get you something else.

34:25.000 --> 34:26.630
Girls like you

34:27.070 --> 34:29.280
should wear pretty dresses.

34:31.239 --> 34:32.630
I know that store.

34:33.230 --> 34:34.400
But it doesn't sell clothes—

34:34.400 --> 34:35.360
it sells identities.

34:35.360 --> 34:36.630
But a new identity is too expensive.

34:36.630 --> 34:37.880
I don't have that money.

34:37.880 --> 34:39.480
Who says we don't have money?

34:40.370 --> 34:41.690
I have plenty.

34:42.290 --> 34:43.620
When we entered the game,

34:43.620 --> 34:45.460
Mr. Guangming gave me his props.

34:46.030 --> 34:47.440
He's just too kind.

34:47.760 --> 34:49.110
It's just a game,

34:49.230 --> 34:50.710
yet he takes such good care of me.

34:50.710 --> 34:52.320
Someone as reliable as him—

34:52.560 --> 34:55.080
his company is bound to succeed.

34:55.389 --> 34:57.250
Wang is in the early stage of his startup.

34:57.250 --> 34:59.190
I want to provide all the support I can,

34:59.190 --> 35:00.360
and help him secure

35:00.360 --> 35:01.710
any potential clients.

35:02.710 --> 35:04.370
Alright, let's go take a look.

35:04.850 --> 35:05.780
This way, Ms. Hu.

35:09.930 --> 35:10.700
Welcome.

35:14.130 --> 35:14.880
How about this one?

35:14.880 --> 35:16.680
A young lady who studied abroad.

35:21.020 --> 35:22.060
This one's nice.

35:22.230 --> 35:23.280
A nurse.

35:23.610 --> 35:25.740
Saving lives and helping the wounded.

35:29.070 --> 35:30.000
This looks good.

35:31.720 --> 35:33.190
When playing this kind of game,

35:33.190 --> 35:34.420
you need to wear clothes like these.

35:34.420 --> 35:35.820
That's what makes it fun,

35:36.360 --> 35:36.880
right?

35:38.210 --> 35:39.410
Just a moment, Ms. Hu.

35:42.000 --> 35:42.730
Try this one.

35:43.400 --> 35:44.230
Size S.

35:44.860 --> 35:45.840
A qipao

35:45.840 --> 35:47.150
is meant to show the curves.

35:47.150 --> 35:48.880
That's what makes it look good.

36:00.000 --> 36:00.760
Mr. Qian.

36:01.200 --> 36:02.630
When I came in just now,

36:03.070 --> 36:04.070
I noticed

36:04.070 --> 36:06.280
an indigo suit on that rack.

36:06.630 --> 36:07.550
It's just as good as any big brand

36:07.550 --> 36:08.750
and really suits you.

36:09.950 --> 36:11.360
Why don't you try it on?

36:12.060 --> 36:14.820
If you wear it, you'll totally
outshine all the other players.

36:14.820 --> 36:15.900
Really?

36:16.630 --> 36:18.230
Alright, I'll go take a look.

36:20.590 --> 36:22.900
All of our suits
are made with the finest fabrics,

36:22.900 --> 36:24.960
and the craftsmanship is excellent.

36:27.260 --> 36:28.010
Ms. Hu,

36:28.400 --> 36:30.330
which suit were you talking about?

36:31.370 --> 36:32.120
Ms. Hu?

36:34.960 --> 36:35.670
Ms. Hu?

37:06.220 --> 37:08.820
Reporter Han,
what brings you to a movie today?

37:15.090 --> 37:16.550
I'm here for an interview.

37:17.000 --> 37:17.730
That's rare.

37:18.440 --> 37:19.320
Rare how?

37:19.990 --> 37:22.550
I invited you
to the military office for an interview,

37:22.550 --> 37:25.110
but you ignored me for days,
Miss Reporter.

37:30.960 --> 37:32.630
What invitation?

37:32.940 --> 37:36.440
It clearly says here that Reporter Han
requested a meeting with Qin Xiaoyi.

37:36.440 --> 37:38.910
When has Qin Xiaoyi
ever been the one to reach out first?

37:38.910 --> 37:40.440
Let's start, Reporter Han.

37:42.060 --> 37:43.140
General Qin,

37:43.160 --> 37:45.840
don't you need
to check my press credentials first?

37:45.840 --> 37:46.590
No need.

37:49.070 --> 37:51.070
It's pitch-dark in this theater.

37:51.070 --> 37:53.320
You can't even see my face clearly,

37:53.510 --> 37:55.710
and you're not
confirming my identity either.

37:55.710 --> 37:57.950
Aren't you afraid
I'm using the title of reporter

37:57.950 --> 37:59.360
to do something shady?

38:03.460 --> 38:05.580
I never allow anyone I don't trust

38:05.700 --> 38:06.940
to come near me.

38:08.410 --> 38:10.140
As a member of the project team,

38:10.230 --> 38:12.190
you should keep a distance from them.

38:12.190 --> 38:13.280
During this project,

38:13.280 --> 38:15.520
it's best to stay away from their people.

38:15.520 --> 38:17.780
The competition for the mayor is fierce.

38:17.880 --> 38:19.590
Aren't you afraid that one day

38:19.590 --> 38:21.760
someone close to you
might be bought off by your rivals,

38:21.760 --> 38:23.480
or tricked into
leaking critical information,

38:23.480 --> 38:25.680
ruining everything at the last moment?

38:26.320 --> 38:27.360
So, Mr. Xiao,

38:28.200 --> 38:30.240
you came to the site

38:30.260 --> 38:31.790
because you don't trust me?

38:36.480 --> 38:37.070
No.

38:38.360 --> 38:40.000
Everyone around me is smart.

38:41.190 --> 38:42.280
And she knows

38:42.710 --> 38:43.970
who will win in the end.

38:54.190 --> 38:55.630
Reporter Han,
you've finished all your questions.

38:55.630 --> 38:56.960
Now I have a few of my own.

38:57.920 --> 38:59.400
Are you and Mr. Miyazaki

38:59.420 --> 39:00.380
very close?

39:02.440 --> 39:03.770
Why are you asking that?

39:04.860 --> 39:07.230
I saw you two
sticking together at the city gate.

39:07.230 --> 39:08.650
Even between husband and wife,

39:08.650 --> 39:10.220
the husband doesn't always

39:10.250 --> 39:11.850
stand on the wife's side—

39:12.150 --> 39:13.630
let alone a fake marriage.

39:14.510 --> 39:15.190
I've known for a long time

39:15.190 --> 39:16.880
that he's not on my side.

39:17.110 --> 39:18.680
Sooner or later, he'll betray me.

39:18.680 --> 39:19.610
So, why do you...

39:19.860 --> 39:21.460
I'm doing this for my friend.

39:21.730 --> 39:23.510
My friend has business to discuss

39:23.510 --> 39:24.590
with Mr. Miyazaki.

39:24.850 --> 39:26.950
Otherwise,
I wouldn't bother dealing with him at all.

39:26.950 --> 39:28.800
Your friend needs to rely on him?

39:29.000 --> 39:29.710
It seems

39:29.800 --> 39:31.530
his career is doing quite well.

39:31.650 --> 39:33.650
I don't know how his career is going,

39:33.650 --> 39:34.700
but as a person,

39:35.360 --> 39:36.320
he's just questionable, to say the least.

39:36.320 --> 39:38.480
He doesn't even know what manners are,

39:38.590 --> 39:40.660
and he doesn't
follow Rongcheng's rules either.

39:40.660 --> 39:41.880
Don't let me run into him again.

39:41.880 --> 39:43.030
Otherwise, I won't be able to stop myself
from hitting him.

39:43.030 --> 39:45.230
Then things will get ugly for everyone.

39:45.280 --> 39:45.950
Okay.

39:48.550 --> 39:49.240
What?

39:50.790 --> 39:52.190
I won't let you run into him.
